# Modern Show Pages for Leave & Overtime Requests

Redesign the detail/show pages for leave requests and overtime requests to display richer, more organized information with a modern UI.

## Proposed Changes

### Backend — Eager Load More Relations

#### [MODIFY] [LeaveRequestController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/sistem-manajemen-kepegawaian/app/Http/Controllers/LeaveRequestController.php)
- In the [show()](file:///c:/laragon/www/sistem-manajemen-kepegawaian/app/Http/Controllers/LeaveRequestController.php#186-197) method, eager-load `employee.position`, `employee.department` alongside current [employee](file:///c:/laragon/www/sistem-manajemen-kepegawaian/app/Models/OvertimeRequest.php#21-25) and [leaveType](file:///c:/laragon/www/sistem-manajemen-kepegawaian/app/Models/LeaveRequest.php#27-31).
- Add computed fields: `total_days` (diffInDays + 1), `created_at` timestamp.

#### [MODIFY] [OvertimeRequestController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/sistem-manajemen-kepegawaian/app/Http/Controllers/OvertimeRequestController.php)
- In the [show()](file:///c:/laragon/www/sistem-manajemen-kepegawaian/app/Http/Controllers/LeaveRequestController.php#186-197) method, eager-load `employee.position`, `employee.department`.
- Add `created_at` timestamp.

---

### Frontend — Leave Request Show Page

#### [MODIFY] [show.tsx](file:///c:/laragon/www/sistem-manajemen-kepegawaian/resources/js/pages/leave-requests/show.tsx)

**New layout structure:**
1. **Status Header Banner** — Full-width colored banner (green/yellow/red) with status icon, label, and request ID.
2. **Employee Info Card** — Initials avatar, full name, position, department.
3. **Detail Grid (2 columns):**
   - Jenis Cuti (with badge)
   - Tanggal Mulai → Tanggal Selesai (with arrow icon, formatted nicely)
   - **Total Hari** (computed: `end_date - start_date + 1`)
   - **Tanggal Pengajuan** (`created_at` formatted)
4. **Alasan Cuti** — Full-width section with quote-style box.
5. **Lampiran** — If exists, show clickable preview/link.
6. **Approval Actions** — Kept at top-right (same as now) for pending requests.

---

### Frontend — Overtime Request Show Page

#### [MODIFY] [show.tsx](file:///c:/laragon/www/sistem-manajemen-kepegawaian/resources/js/pages/overtime-requests/show.tsx)

**New layout structure:**
1. **Status Header Banner** — Same pattern as leave.
2. **Employee Info Card** — Initials avatar, full name, position, department.
3. **Detail Grid (2–3 columns):**
   - Tanggal Lembur
   - Waktu Mulai & Waktu Selesai (displayed side-by-side)
   - **Durasi Lembur** — Computed from `start_time` and `end_time` (e.g., "1 jam 30 menit")
   - **Tanggal Pengajuan** (`created_at` formatted)
4. **Deskripsi/Tugas** — Full-width section with styled box.
5. **Approval Actions** — Same placement.

---

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `./vendor/bin/pest --filter LeaveRequestTest` and `--filter OvertimeRequestTest`.

### Manual Verification
- Navigate to a leave request detail page and verify all new fields display correctly.
- Navigate to an overtime request detail page and verify duration calculation is correct.
